Package: mltools
Type: Package
Title: Machine Learning Tools
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Ben Gorman
Maintainer: Ben Gorman <bgorman@GormAnalysis.com>
Description: mltools is simply a collection of utility and helper methods for machine learning. It relies heavily on the data.table package, and some methods rely on the Matrix package for handling sparse data.
